826
00:42:31,833 --> 00:42:33,533
笙ｪThis time?笙ｪ

827
00:42:41,833 --> 00:42:43,133
笙ｪEven the strongest heart笙ｪ

828
00:42:43,267 --> 00:42:44,933
笙ｪCan waver笙ｪ

