00:42:45,167 --> 00:42:48,367
笙ｪAnd doubt its fire笙ｪ

830
00:42:48,633 --> 00:42:50,267
笙ｪBut you never lost faith in me笙ｪ

831
00:42:50,267 --> 00:42:51,933
笙ｪIn every battle, every dream I chased笙ｪ

832
00:42:52,133 --> 00:42:54,833
笙ｪThere is meaning in every step I made笙ｪ

833
00:42:55,667 --> 00:43:01,633
笙ｪThrough the storm, through the endless night笙ｪ

834
00:43:01,967 --> 00:43:03,633
笙ｪYou were there, shining like a light笙ｪ

835
00:43:03,633 --> 00:43:05,300
笙ｪWarm and bright笙ｪ

836
00:43:05,467 --> 00:43:09,167
